c=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e84e82e645574a34cb4e83365b9361739562a3f","tid":38772,"uid":13294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T07:34:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>養鬼仔咪姐係佛牌類似既野   唔好同我講咩正牌邪牌    <span style=\"color: red;\">用到屍油同塊就係養鬼仔</span> <br />\n<br />\n身邊有人養過    開頭真係唔錯   事事順景 <br />\n佢仲要開麻雀檔   啲人好似倒水咁上去輸錢 <br />\n但最大問題係送唔走   最尾係輸翻轉頭</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n即係邪牌效果好但難送走？<br />\n正牌就效果細但係易送就？<br />\n<br />\n洗唔洗餵？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同時放個十字架係屋企會點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你意思係佛牌都係鬼仔一種？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03b773c1e6f2db814566f56d38bda7ae3e52b234","tid":38772,"uid":6313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T07:36:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>大個咪變鬼佬</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9a7eae1118f2cb78f16b868f80b3c099a1bc7c8","tid":38772,"uid":1557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T07:43:00.000Z","msg":"好似要餵血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"373b4332aaefc89b3b7b1d3537e5fbc39feade15","tid":38772,"uid":65225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T08:33:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>養鬼仔咪姐係佛牌類似既野   唔好同我講咩正牌邪牌    <span style=\"color: red;\">用到屍油同塊就係養鬼仔</span> <br />\n<br />\n身邊有人養過    開頭真係唔